		<title>John Oliver No Longer White: Oliver’s Membership to Malan Race Confirmed</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/ColorBlindPodshout/~3/DZXv3zzen7U/</link>
		<comments>http://iammalan.org/wordpress/?p=26#comments</comments>
